&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LOS-ANGELES-BOULEVARD-3-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8343&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LOS-ANGELES-BOULEVARD-3-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LOS ANGELES- BOULEVARD 3- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;177&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Boulevard 3 is Located in the heart of Hollywood in the location of the former Hollywood Athletic Club. Three areas each with their own bar and distinct design in accordance with that of Manor-like residence; a garden, a library and a multi-level Grand Ballroom equipped with a stage built over the bar that provides a dance show throughout the night. Attire is upscale trendy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book &lt;a href=&quot;http://boulevard3.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;contact Boulevard 3 by phone at +&lt;a href=&quot;tel:3234662144&quot;&gt;323 466 2144&lt;/a&gt; or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reservations@boulevard3.com&quot;&gt;reservations@boulevard3.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For table service only, Boulevard 3 requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation. You will be provided with pricing for the table you reserve. A credit card authorization form will be sent at the time of booking to be filled in and returned back.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled 48 hours prior to the scheduled date or in the event of a no-show, a 50% fee to the agreed upon (at the time of booking) minimum will be charged to the credit card on file.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating nightclub/lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

